。\r\n                                      書記官  林廷佳\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　 1 　月　　 27　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/108%2c%e9%87%91%e4%b8%8a%e9%87%8d%e6%9b%b4%e4%b8%80%2c7%2c20220127%2c5/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,108,金上重更一,7,20220127,5","JYEAR":"108","JCASE":"金上重更一","JNO":"7","JDATE":"20220127","JTITLE":"證券交易法"}